                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1206539193" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1206539193">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/caihaoruo/">梦回明清</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2017-06-26</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">见路不走确实高级。但是作为小说，有些情节不是很合理。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1204758816">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1204758816" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1204758816" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1204758816">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/70440342/">逆光的眼睛</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-06-19</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">虽然豆豆三部小说都是一样的模式，可三部小说我都爱。这是最后一部，期待豆豆能重回视线。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1201143645">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1201143645" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1201143645" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1201143645">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/136891005/">张亮1119</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-06-11</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">能把一本小说写到情节已经不在重要，完全靠叶子农一个人的思想来撑起整体框架的程度，作者绝非一般水准。人生在世，能活的通透很难，通透之后仍然保持着底线和立场更难，愿意为了立场牺牲自己则是难上加难。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1199753609">
